<template >
    <v-row no-gutters>
        <v-flex class="ml-3" v-if="notTryOut">
         Welcome, {{this.$store.getters.getUsername}}
        </v-flex>
        <v-flex class="ml-3" v-if="tryOut">
            Welcome Guest
        </v-flex>
<v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <v-card class = "mr-3 pa-1" @click="logout" :-if="notTryOut">
            Logout
        </v-card>
        
    </v-row>
</template>

<script>


export default {
    name : "StatusBar",
    methods : {
        logout(){
            this.$store.dispatch("logout")
            .then(() => {
                this.$router.push("/")
            })
        }
    },
    computed : {
        notTryOut() {
            return !this.$store.getters.inTryOutMode
        },
        tryOut() {
            return this.$store.getters.inTryOutMode
        }
    }

}
</script>

<style scoped>


</style>
